laboratory_examinations.findings: Negative for Neisseria Gonorrhoeae by PCR.

Fluid filled, dilated appendix up to 8 mm in diameter with hyperenhancing walls and mild surrounding fat stranding and fluid. No free air, no free fluid, no evidence of fluid collection or perforation.
WBC count 11.2 K/uL, which is outside the normal range (normal range: 4.0 - 11.0 K/uL).
